ÝROTARY
INTERNATIONAL
This bench, and the nearby tree, were placed here
to commemorate the centenary of the
ROTARY CLUB OF WALSALL
which was inaugurated on 5 October 1921 - local people
coming together to serve the community of Walsall
and internationally.
